    "description": "ARMS DOLL是一款VR机甲动作游戏，你将成为一个名为ARMS DOLL的人形移动武器的飞行员，与敌人作战。<br><br>玩家使用驾驶舱控制器控制ARMS DOLL来执行任务。<br>然后，玩家可以用完成任务赚来的钱来购买新的机器和武器，并在执行更多的任务时加强他们手中的装备。<br> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1877800/extras/4dbd628e6e68c16fd881033340d60654.poster.avif?t=1690698063\" width=480 height=272 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1877800/extras/4dbd628e6e68c16fd881033340d60654.webm?t=1690698063\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1877800/extras/4dbd628e6e68c16fd881033340d60654.mp4?t=1690698063\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>有性能均衡的中量级机器，有高机动性以躲避敌人攻击的轻量级机器，有强大装甲以抵御攻击的重量级机器，还有价格低廉的小型机器和性能较差的工作机器。<br>玩家可以登上许多不同的机器，它们会在任务中作为敌人出现。<br> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1877800/extras/70f286e1f99367ec5ac450fa143b6efe.poster.avif?t=1690698063\" width=480 height=272 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1877800/extras/70f286e1f99367ec5ac450fa143b6efe.webm?t=1690698063\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1877800/extras/70f286e1f99367ec5ac450fa143b6efe.mp4?t=1690698063\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>而基本上，ARMS DOLL可以在双手和肩上携带武器，这些武器的组合将大大改变他们的战斗方式。<br>为任务或根据玩家的喜好选择最好的机器和武器。<br> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1877800/extras/71cf2649231fde8c7d3c2148efaa2306.poster.avif?t=1690698063\" width=480 height=272 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1877800/extras/71cf2649231fde8c7d3c2148efaa2306.webm?t=1690698063\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1877800/extras/71cf2649231fde8c7d3c2148efaa2306.mp4?t=1690698063\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>有时，你会面对载有王牌飞行员的定制机器，或神秘的大型武器。<br>所有这些都是强大的对手，但通过加强你的机器并找出与之对抗的方法，你将能够获胜。<br> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1877800/extras/a901904fc0509d424c5f18d3e27e53db.poster.avif?t=1690698063\" width=480 height=272 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1877800/extras/a901904fc0509d424c5f18d3e27e53db.webm?t=1690698063\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1877800/extras/a901904fc0509d424c5f18d3e27e53db.mp4?t=1690698063\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
